title: Tex-Mex Burgers
directions: Combine all ingredients in a bowl and use hands to mix well. Form mixture into patties.
Cook on a grill or in a pan on the stovetop, until cooked to desired doneness.
ingredients: 1/2 lbs. beef, ground, free-range or grass-fed, organic
1/4 c. bell pepper, red, fresh, organic
1/2 tsp. sea salt, unrefined and pure
